        "timestamp": "2020-04-06 12:32:50.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWe have been having issues with the naming service not starting in the Orange lab (used for testing updates to OOM).  Unfortunately, we can't see why it is failing because logs were being redirected to a file in /tmp on the failed pod - which of course is inaccessible because it is in a failed state.\n\nUpdated the start script for naming service to use tee to write to stdout/stderr as usual, but also save a copy in the same files it was redirecting to before.",
        "patchset_number": 1
